ortant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bott=
om-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  story in brief</a>. AMC Enterta=
inment Holdings Inc. became=C2=A0a meme-stock company and=C2=A0sold a lot o=
f stock to retail investors to raise money to buy, among other things, <a h=
ref=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32175659.262414/aHR0cH=
M6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDMtMTUvYW1jLWJvd=
