feel a little bit like all of recent financial history has been leading up =
to this moment.=E2=80=9D For instance, =E2=80=9Cmeme stocks have prepared e=
veryone for the notion that the value of a stock is based on the fervor of =
its community of online fans, not its projected cash flows.=E2=80=9D TMTG i=
s the purest form of meme stock: It launched as a meme stock before it was =
actually a company, and used its meme-stock status to sort of, maybe, boots=
trap its way into being a company.</p>
