DeSantis wrote in the letter to Lamar Taylor, the interim director of the S=
tate Board of Administration, the state agency that manages Florida=E2=80=
=99s retirement funds for public workers. DeSantis oversees the board as a =
trustee along with the state=E2=80=99s attorney general and chief financial=
