<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Speaking to Fox News on Thursday night about t=
he letter, DeSantis said the state may consider a =E2=80=9Cderivative lawsu=
it=E2=80=9D against AB InBev. Derivative lawsuits are filed by shareholders=
